fields.name: ActionSet
fields.description: Set of actions to be done as part of the rewrite Rule.

fields.name: Conditions
fields.description: Conditions based on which the action set execution will be evaluated.

fields.name: Name
fields.description: Name of the rewrite rule that is unique within an Application Gateway.

fields.name: RuleSequence
fields.description: Rule Sequence of the rewrite rule that determines the order of execution of a particular rule in a RewriteRuleSet.
